data.description: PRICE REDUCED AND READY TO SELL!!! Simply adorable!!!  Are you looking for 4 bdrms , 2 bath, 1990 Sf of well distributed space to reflect spacious rooms? Well, as you enter the home the hallway is a pallet waiting  to be designed . Now the living room is open to the kitchen/ dining and boasts large windows that overlook the backyard, and a stone fireplace that accentuates this adorable home. Enjoy evenings and holidays in the well appointed kitchen that has lots of cabinet and counterspace to allow family meal planning or just a great dinner at home. The primary suite is,(more than an oasis )with an area to design for relaxation or additional privacy away from the family. The primary bathroom features double vanity, soaking tub, and a separate shower that is perfect for relaxation after a long day.3 additional bedrooms are spacious with walk-in closets and ceiling fans. The backyard allows room for barbecues or games with friends. This home is a must see and priced to SELL schedule an appointment to view this property today.
